Question: The left image shows a stack of at least four round patties topped with a dollop of white cream and sprinkled with green ring shapes, all on a white dish.

Reference Answer: True

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there at least four round patties on the dish?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the cream dollop white?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the ring shapes green?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
